Installation
============

In order to install this plugin you will require the Java Development Tools.
Follow the following steps to install Java Development Tools:
	
	1. Go to Help->Install New Software
	2. On the drop down select The Eclipse Project Updates - http://download.eclipse.org/eclipse/updates/4.3
	3. Select the Java Development Tools.
	4. Install.
	
Once Java Development Tools is installed, locate the jar file under plugin/plugins directory. 
Locate the directory that you installed eclipse and find the "dropins" folder. 
Take the jar and drop it in the "dropins" folder.